	</div>

	<div id="t_196_3" style="position: absolute; left: 8.82%; top:17.87%;" class="c_196_1">
		Jefferson and adopted by
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_4" style="position: absolute; left: 8.82%; top:20.26%;" class="c_196_1">
		the Second Continental
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_5" style="position: absolute; left: 8.82%; top:22.66%;" class="c_196_1">
		Congress July 4, 1776.
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_6" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:29.62%;" class="c_196_2">
		Jefferson states his ideas
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_7" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:31.13%;" class="c_196_2">
		about government.
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_8" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:32.88%;" class="c_196_3">
		All people have certain rights
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_9" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:34.40%;" class="c_196_3">
		and freedoms that no one can
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_10" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:35.91%;" class="c_196_3">
		take away. Governments get
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_11" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:37.43%;" class="c_196_3">
		their power from the people
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_12" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:38.94%;" class="c_196_3">
		and are formed to protect
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_13" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:40.46%;" class="c_196_3">
		these rights and freedoms. If
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_14" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:41.97%;" class="c_196_3">
		the government acts in a way
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_15" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:43.49%;" class="c_196_3">
		that hurts the people and
	</div>

	<div id="t_196_16" style="position: absolute; left: 8.52%; top:45.00%;" class="c_196_3">
